with start_station_groups as (
    
    select 
        start_station_name as citibike_station_name, 
        start_station_id as citibike_station_id, 
        round(start_lat, 6) as station_latitude, 
        round(start_lng, 6) as station_longitude
    from combined_years
    group by
        start_station_name, 
        start_station_id, 
        round(start_lat, 6), 
        round(start_lng, 6) 

),

end_station_groups as (
    
    select 
        end_station_name as citibike_station_name, 
        end_station_id as citibike_station_id, 
        round(end_lat, 6) as station_latitude, 
        round(end_lng, 6) as station_longitude
    from combined_years
    group by
        end_station_name, 
        end_station_id, 
        round(end_lat, 6), 
        round(end_lng, 6) 

),

all_station_groups as (
    select * from start_station_groups
    union
    select * from end_station_groups
)

select

with cte as (
    select
        citibike_station_name,
        citibike_station_id,
        station_latitude,
        station_longitude
    from "dev"."main"."station_geographies"
),

in_polygon as (
    select
        cte.*,
        exists(
            select 1
            from utils.cpz_polygons as poly
            where st_within(
                st_point(cte.station_longitude, cte.station_latitude),
                poly.geometry
            )
        ) as in_cpz
    from cte
),

converted as (
    select
        citibike_station_id,
        station_latitude,
        station_longitude,
        case
            when in_cpz is true then 'inside'
            else 'outside'
        end as in_cpz
    from in_polygon
),

find_spread as (
    select
        citibike_station_id,
        in_cpz,
        count(*) as count_instances
    from converted
    group by
        citibike_station_id,
        in_cpz
),

pivoted as (
    pivot find_spread
    on in_cpz in ('inside', 'outside')
    using coalesce(sum(count_instances), 0)
    group by citibike_station_id
)

select
    citibike_station_id,
    case
        when abs(subtract(inside, outside)) < 100 then false
        when
            abs(subtract(inside, outside)) >= 100 and inside > outside
            then true
        when
            abs(subtract(inside, outside)) >= 100 and inside < outside
            then false
    end as in_cpz
from pivoted

select start_station_id
from "dev"."main"."fct_citibike_rides_by_ym"
where start_station_id is null

with child as (
    select start_station_id as from_field
    from "dev"."main"."fct_citibike_rides_by_ym"
    where start_station_id is not null
),

parent as (
    select citibike_station_id as to_field
    from "dev"."main"."dim_citibike_stations"
)

select
    from_field

from child
left join parent
    on child.from_field = parent.to_field

where parent.to_field is null

select
    start_station_id as unique_field,
    count(*) as n_records

from "dev"."main"."fct_citibike_rides_by_ym"
where start_station_id is not null
group by start_station_id
having count(*) > 1
